WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.310
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:04.230
Lord. Thank you for joining me today. I

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:06.950
have my sweetheart with me again. I have

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:11.830
a very sobering word,

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:13.990
is what I want to call it,

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.870
for what the Lord has given me today.

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:18.950
It's very heavy;

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.029
it's correction

00:00:21.039 --> 00:00:23.910
for the body. But

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:26.070
whenever you get a word like this, and

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:28.870
you see into the future,

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:30.790
and you see hearts,

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:34.069
there was so much the Lord showed me

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:35.750
driving around when I was praying

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:42.630
over our city today.

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:44.549
Quite frankly, I don't

00:00:44.559 --> 00:00:47.590
even know where to start or how to

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:51.270
even bring this up

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:53.910
because of how correction was said and

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.069
what the Lord said. So, I'm asking the

00:00:56.079 --> 00:00:59.910
Holy Spirit for help right now. I

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:02.069
want to deliver it accurately, and

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:04.070
I want to deliver it with none of

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:05.670
Brandon,

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:09.109
all of Jesus.

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:15.270
Okay, so this is what I saw.

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:20.390
I saw a great economic crisis coming.

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:23.190
I haven't

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:27.109
seen this in a while: an economic

00:01:27.109 --> 00:01:27.119
1930s-style

00:01:27.119 --> 00:01:31.190
crash on steroids. All I've

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:33.670
seen was this blessing,

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:36.469
but the Lord brought the blessing in

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:41.030
with the crash again. And as I

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:44.789
was driving around, I could

00:01:44.789 --> 00:01:44.799
see—the

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:47.429
Lord said, 'What you see is poor now.

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:50.069
There will be no middle class

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:52.310
in the days ahead. There will be no

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:54.789
middle class. There will be poor, and

00:01:54.799 --> 00:01:57.350
there'll be extreme poor, and then there

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:59.510
will be

00:01:59.510 --> 00:01:59.520
rich.'He

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:02.149
said, 'What you see right now—as you

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:03.990
see what you consider the people who

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:06.310
work at McDonald's, Taco Bell

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:07.830
employees, maybe making a little bit

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:10.550
above minimum wage,

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:12.710
would be considered the middle class in

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:16.070
the days ahead. And what we consider

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:17.910
poor

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:24.949
will be so poor that I saw

00:02:24.959 --> 00:02:27.990
what I can only describe as poverty

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:32.470
like I've never seen before in

00:02:32.470 --> 00:02:32.480
America.'As

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:35.030
I was driving around, I was having an

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:37.030
open-eyed vision, and I was actually

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:40.630
seeing the way it was in future

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:43.509
time, in real-time, driving around. And I

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:44.949
can tell you, I've never done this

00:02:44.959 --> 00:02:46.790
before.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:49.509
I could see tent cities of

00:02:49.519 --> 00:02:51.350
homeless people walking

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:53.430
around. Like when you go to LA and you

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:56.229
see a homeless street like Skid Row, this

00:02:56.239 --> 00:02:59.110
was everywhere.

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:02.790
And I can tell you, I saw the housing

00:03:02.800 --> 00:03:05.910
crisis coming again with people not

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:08.070
being able to pay their

00:03:08.070 --> 00:03:08.080
mortgages—not

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:10.470
just a couple hundred people, I'm

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:12.630
talking thousands upon thousands of

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:14.309
people not being able to pay their

00:03:14.319 --> 00:03:16.869
mortgages or their car loans. And there

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:20.309
was foreclosure everywhere,

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:22.630
to the point where I was wondering

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:24.949
who was not foreclosing on

00:03:24.959 --> 00:03:27.270
their houses. Like I said, there was no

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:31.030
middle class. There was poor, there

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:32.710
was extreme poor, and then there was

00:03:32.710 --> 00:03:32.720
the

00:03:32.720 --> 00:03:35.030
rich. But there was a Robin Hood

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:38.309
mentality that I saw.

00:03:38.319 --> 00:03:40.710
There was such a hatred towards the

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:43.589
rich. And what I saw in rich

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:45.990
neighborhoods was that they had security,

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:48.710
armed security, around their houses and

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:51.670
around their property at all times

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:54.070
because the people would loot them and

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:56.949
steal from them. And there were certain

00:03:56.959 --> 00:03:58.869
streets that we were driving down

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:00.789
that I knew, that the Lord showed

00:04:00.799 --> 00:04:02.470
me in the future, it would not be

00:04:02.480 --> 00:04:06.309
safe for women to go on those streets.

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:09.830
To the point where right now there

00:04:09.830 --> 00:04:09.840
are

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:12.309
malls there, there are nice

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:14.470
restaurants there, and the Lord showed

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:16.229
me that there would be times in the

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:18.069
future that you could not be a woman and

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:21.349
go down these streets at night at all.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:26.870
As I drove around, he said to me, 'Woe,

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:30.710
America, I have favored you above all

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:33.990
other nations with prosperity. I

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.950
have held you in my hand. I have held

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:39.830
you in my hand.'It was the way

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:43.510
that the blessing was on

00:04:43.510 --> 00:04:43.520
America—the

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:46.070
favor and the blessing that has been on

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:48.469
our nation.

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:51.990
And I saw, as I was driving around, a

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.390
shaking of finances beyond anything I've

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:57.670
ever seen before. But he talked to

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:00.550
me about the wave of blessing, this

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:03.430
window of opportunity, and how he said,

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:06.469
'Brandon, even I, even my wife, we've

00:05:06.479 --> 00:05:08.469
got to come up even higher in the fire

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:10.390
to listen to what he's asking and

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:13.350
instructing us to do.'I saw people

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:16.629
fleeing the city again, and masses going

00:05:16.639 --> 00:05:19.510
to rural land and having places

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:22.310
of getaway because of how bad it was. I

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:24.230
saw people pillaging grocery stores,

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:27.590
pillaging farmers'fields

00:05:27.590 --> 00:05:27.600
and

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:30.310
tractors. I'm talking

00:05:30.320 --> 00:05:32.550
it looked like something out of a

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:35.990
Mad Max movie,

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:38.469
the way the people were acting. And

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:40.950
like I said, I've never seen

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:43.590
poverty like I saw in these visions as I

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:45.590
was driving around praying over our

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:48.550
city.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:51.110
This is Oklahoma;

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:52.790
I can't even imagine what it looked like

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:55.830
up north. But the Lord said,

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:57.990
'You took part of the

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:01.110
word that I said to you about

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.950
there being glory events instead of

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:04.870
sporting events, and you just kind

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:07.029
of bypassed it. You didn't think into

00:06:07.039 --> 00:06:09.270
what I was telling you, that the people

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:11.830
would not have finances to go to a

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:13.909
sporting event in the days ahead, and

00:06:13.919 --> 00:06:16.309
that these major sporting teams would

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:19.189
have to file bankruptcy

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:21.510
because they were not able to pay their

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:24.950
big sports teams their salaries.

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:28.070
The major contracts that were signed

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:30.390
concerning some of these major players,

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:32.710
they won't be able to afford them

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:35.270
because the teams will not have

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:37.749
support from

00:06:37.749 --> 00:06:37.759
the fans.'So,

00:06:37.759 --> 00:06:40.550
I saw again the Lord speaking to me

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:42.469
about major teams,

00:06:42.479 --> 00:06:44.790
sporting event teams, that will file

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:47.350
bankruptcy because of what's coming in

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:49.029
the near future.

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:51.270
We have a window of opportunity the Lord

00:06:51.280 --> 00:06:53.830
is giving us to listen to

00:06:53.840 --> 00:06:56.230
him for the wealth transfer.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.990
What qualifies you for the wealth

00:06:58.000 --> 00:06:59.990
transfer? And the Lord gave you specific

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:02.550
instructions about sowing and what cost

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:05.830
you something versus bucket plunkers

00:07:05.830 --> 00:07:05.840
where

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.510
you just give a couple hundred bucks

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:08.790
and you think, 'Well, I qualified for the

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:10.309
wealth transfer,'and the Lord said, 'That's

00:07:10.319 --> 00:07:12.629
not what qualifies. The

00:07:12.629 --> 00:07:12.639
one percent

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:16.469
will walk in this.'And I saw

00:07:16.479 --> 00:07:19.909
again today the heart of the church as a

00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:22.469
whole. I'm not going to say it's each

00:07:22.479 --> 00:07:24.230
individual person. I'm saying as a

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:27.029
whole. Okay? It's fair; this

00:07:27.039 --> 00:07:31.189
is fair. I saw an apple that

00:07:31.199 --> 00:07:33.270
looked

00:07:33.280 --> 00:07:35.270
gorgeous on the

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:36.790
outside.

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:39.749
And this apple was just juicy looking.

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:41.430
But the Lord said, 'I want to take you

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:43.830
to the core of what this fruit really is

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:46.150
and the fruit of the church as a whole

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:49.430
in America.'And it was rotten at the

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:52.870
core; it was rotten on the inside.

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:55.029
Everything that was displayed on the

00:07:55.039 --> 00:07:58.309
inside looked like rotten sludge; it was

00:07:58.319 --> 00:08:01.749
black and putrid and nasty, and it was

00:08:01.759 --> 00:08:04.309
just so disgusting. But the further it

00:08:04.319 --> 00:08:06.309
went on the outside, and the display of

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:08.469
what it tried to display itself, was

00:08:08.479 --> 00:08:10.710
beautiful and lush. But when you took a

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:13.430
bite out of it, it wasn't the first bite

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:15.749
that was bad. It was after you

00:08:15.759 --> 00:08:17.589
bit it several times and then you

00:08:17.599 --> 00:08:19.510
got to the center. And the closer you

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:21.430
got to the center of the core of the

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:24.790
church, it was rotten.

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:26.309
And the Lord said, 'I want you to see

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:29.270
what I see. I want you to see what

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:32.070
comes before me as you ask for

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:35.190
revival, but yet I'm trying to

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:37.509
bring healing at a certain church,

00:08:37.519 --> 00:08:39.190
but you're too

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:43.029
concerned about

00:08:43.029 --> 00:08:43.039
timeframes.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:45.750
It's not convenient. And what I'm about

00:08:45.760 --> 00:08:48.470
to do in this end-time outpouring will

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:51.829
not be convenient to you—the

00:08:51.829 --> 00:08:51.839
30-minute

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:54.949
services, maybe the hour services. Well,

00:08:54.959 --> 00:08:57.430
you know, we had service two days ago,

00:08:57.440 --> 00:08:59.590
but you know, we prayed for the revival

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:01.990
and a couple of people got saved. And

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.070
yet we are interceding

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:06.230
and we're wanting so much, but yet we

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:08.710
want to give so

00:09:08.710 --> 00:09:08.720
little.'And

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:11.030
the Lord showed me there's so much

00:09:11.030 --> 00:09:11.040
in

00:09:11.040 --> 00:09:14.310
the hearts of the leaders. I saw

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:17.350
people that were something in the past

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:20.790
trying to be Sauls,

00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:24.070
asking to present themselves as if the

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:26.389
anointing and the glory was still there.

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:28.630
But the Lord said, 'It's a great

00:09:28.630 --> 00:09:28.640
Ichabod

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:30.630
coming.

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:32.710
There's a great Ichabod coming on a lot of

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.070
these people, and they don't even know the

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:36.389
glory has departed.

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:38.630
The glory has departed. Their

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:41.110
heart is far from me.'What you're about

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:43.509
to see is this scripture come to full

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:45.829
manifestation,

00:09:45.839 --> 00:09:47.750
and the church has never

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:49.670
seen this before.

00:09:49.680 --> 00:09:51.190
And so I want you to read this

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.150
scripture, baby.

00:09:52.160 --> 00:09:55.110
It says, 'And because iniquity

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.590
shall abound, the love of many shall wax

00:09:57.590 --> 00:09:57.600
cold.'And

00:09:57.600 --> 00:10:00.949
that's Matthew.

00:10:00.959 --> 00:10:05.110
'But he that shall endure until the end,

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:08.150
the same shall be saved.'And this gospel

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:10.150
of the kingdom shall be preached

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:10.160
in

00:10:10.160 --> 00:10:12.230
all the world for a witness unto all

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:14.710
nations, and then the end shall come.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:17.110
So we're at that place right now. What

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:18.949
He started talking to

00:10:18.959 --> 00:10:21.350
us about is that the love of many will

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:23.990
wax cold, and He said you're going to see

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:25.509
pillaging and you're going to see people

00:10:25.519 --> 00:10:27.269
in the body of Christ do things that you

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:31.430
never thought you would see,

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:36.550
with a turning on people. I saw

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:38.949
it. When He used that scripture, I

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:41.509
saw the way it was with people, and the

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:44.069
way they were not safe to go to

00:10:44.079 --> 00:10:46.710
Walmart.

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:49.110
It was rough. The visions that I

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.790
had today were rough. And I'm telling

00:10:50.800 --> 00:10:54.150
you, it shook me because He was

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:56.150
talking about all these people

00:10:56.150 --> 00:10:56.160
who

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:57.910
say they're all in, who are in

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.350
upper leadership. They've been there, and

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:01.910
they have this sense of,

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:03.829
'I've been there, I've done

00:11:03.839 --> 00:11:05.990
that, I have had the glory on me in

00:11:05.990 --> 00:11:06.000
the past.'And

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.829
they want to pretend that

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:09.990
they're still on the vine, but the heart

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:12.389
of who they really are has

00:11:12.389 --> 00:11:12.399
waxed

00:11:12.399 --> 00:11:16.550
cold, and they are no longer that vessel

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:20.069
that is on fire for Him. They have an

00:11:20.079 --> 00:11:22.230
entitlement:

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:23.990
'I've been

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:25.670
there, I've done that,

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:28.150
I'm

00:11:28.150 --> 00:11:28.160
qualified.'But

00:11:28.160 --> 00:11:30.870
I saw a church through the Father's

00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:35.350
eyes that was no longer

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:38.470
desperate and hungry anymore;

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:42.310
they were entitled.

00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:45.910
'You have an hour to do this

00:11:45.920 --> 00:11:48.790
healing room service, two hours at

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:50.710
the most, but if it goes over that, it's

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:52.470
time for my

00:11:52.470 --> 00:11:52.480
bedtime.'But

00:11:52.480 --> 00:11:55.269
people are so desperate for

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:57.829
a touch, and you're a leader, and yet you

00:11:57.839 --> 00:12:01.829
qualify yourself by a clock,

00:12:01.829 --> 00:12:01.839
saying,

00:12:01.839 --> 00:12:03.910
'Well, it's

00:12:03.920 --> 00:12:06.710
too long.'And the Lord said,

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:08.949
'Brandon, what's about to happen will

00:12:08.959 --> 00:12:12.790
not be convenient.

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:14.870
A shaking to awaken is coming to

00:12:14.880 --> 00:12:16.629
America.

00:12:16.639 --> 00:12:18.470
You're about to see something that you

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:21.030
never thought you would

00:12:21.030 --> 00:12:21.040
see.'And

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:23.430
I'm telling you, from sea to shining

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:25.430
sea, we will have a great revival. But

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:28.310
there is no urgency in the

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:30.870
church. The Lord is showing me

00:12:30.870 --> 00:12:30.880
that.

